Package com.github.dm.jrt.android.proxy.builder

Classes and interfaces related to proxy routine builders, specific to the Android platform.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    LoaderProxyObjectBuilder<TYPE>
    Interface defining a builder of async proxy objects, running in dedicated Loaders.
    LoaderProxyRoutineBuilder
    Interface defining a builder of routines wrapping an object methods, running in dedicated Loaders.
    ServiceProxyObjectBuilder<TYPE>
    Interface defining a builder of async proxy objects, whose methods are executed in a dedicated Service.
    ServiceProxyRoutineBuilder
    Interface defining a builder of routines wrapping an object, whose methods are executed in a dedicated Service.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractLoaderProxyObjectBuilder<TYPE>
    Abstract implementation of a builder of async proxy objects, running in dedicated Loaders.
    AbstractServiceProxyObjectBuilder<TYPE>
    Abstract implementation of a builder of async proxy objects, whose methods are executed in a dedicated Service.
